<p>Annexes   
</p>
<p>I. Summary of the expert presentations and initial discussions on the topics of &#8220;Xenophobia&#8221; and 
&#8220;Establishment, designation or maintaining of national mechanisms with competences to protect  
against and prevent all forms and manifestations of racism, racial discrimination, xenophobia  
and related intolerance&#8221; ...................................................................................................................  20 
</p>
