dealing with 
discrimination in sport 
 
</p>
<p>Item 6  
Establishment, designation or 
maintaining of national 
mechanisms with competences to 
protect against and prevent all 
forms and manifestations of 
racism, racial discrimination, 
xenophobia and related intolerance 
Mr. Michel Forst, Secr&#233;taire 
